spec_data.Name: perl-DBICx-AutoDoc
spec_data.Description:
DBICx::AutoDoc is a utility that can automatically generate documentation
for your DBIx::Class schemas. It works by collecting information from
several sources and arranging it into a format that makes it easier to deal
with from templates.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 10:22:32 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Generate automatic documentation of DBIx::Class::Schema objects
